{"kind":"concept","id":12,"concept_type":"Contract","name":"C-2025-001","description":"Master Services Agreement — Contract C-2025-001\r\n\r\nEffective date: January 15, 2025\r\nTerm: 12 months, with automatic renewal for additional 12-month periods\r\nunless either party terminates with 90 days written notice.\r\n\r\nParties:\r\n  - Acme Labs (the \"Provider\"), registered in Lyon, France.\r\n  - Globex (the \"Client\"), registered in Wilmington, Delaware, USA.\r\n\r\nScope:\r\n  Acme Labs will design, build, and integrate a sensor-based industrial\r\n  automation pilot at the Globex Memphis distribution hub. The pilot\r\n  covers the receiving dock and one outbound sortation lane. Deliverables\r\n  include hardware install, firmware, an API for the Globex WMS, and\r\n  on-site training for two operators.\r\n\r\nCommercial terms:\r\n  Total contract value: 50,000 EUR. Billed in two milestone invoices of\r\n  18,000 EUR (Q1) and 32,000 EUR (Q2). Net 30 payment terms.\r\n\r\nSignatories:\r\n  Alice Martin, CTO — Acme Labs\r\n  Bob Chen, VP Operations — Globex\r\n","properties":{}}
