{"kind":"concept","id":11,"concept_type":"Contract","name":"C-2025-002","description":"Logistics Integration Agreement — Contract C-2025-002\r\n\r\nEffective date: April 1, 2025\r\nTerm: 24 months, fixed.\r\n\r\nParties:\r\n  - Globex (the \"Integrator\"), Wilmington, Delaware, USA.\r\n  - Initech (the \"Customer\"), Austin, Texas, USA.\r\n\r\nScope:\r\n  Globex will provide an end-to-end logistics integration for Initech's\r\n  enterprise software supply chain. Work includes a custom REST connector\r\n  between Globex's TMS and Initech's procurement platform, three days of\r\n  on-site training in Austin, and a Q1 retainer covering planning and\r\n  discovery.\r\n\r\nCommercial terms:\r\n  Total contract value: 120,000 EUR for the first 12 months. Billed\r\n  quarterly. Net 45 payment terms. Renewal pricing to be negotiated 60\r\n  days before expiry.\r\n\r\nSignatories:\r\n  Bob Chen, VP Operations — Globex\r\n  Carol Diaz, Head of Procurement — Initech\r\n","properties":{}}
